{"tid":2164684,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"金茶王（2017）冠軍陳偉聰 加盟瓏門冰室","createTime":"2020-08-19T10:36:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T12:54:42.000Z","uid":58335,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"42e505717d2b96540c75da108e4667ccb344ac90","tid":2164684,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T10:36:10.000Z","msg":"睇得出瓏門有心改善食物質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【 公告：金茶王（2017）冠軍陳偉聰 加盟瓏門冰室 】<br />\n<br />\n人大咗<br />\n要向公眾承認自己做得唔夠好<br />\n係一件好難嘅事<br />\n但我更加認為 要對支持自己嘅人負責<br />\n其實香港人一直都畀緊勇氣我去面對自己嘅缺點<br />\n<br />\n「奶茶王」Nelson 多謝你願意助我一臂之力<br />\n加入小弟嘅飲食團隊<br />\n我會努力去做到一間令香港人驕傲嘅冰室<br />\n<br />\n#全新奶茶配方不日上架<br />\n#世界要你努力去考取功名<br />\n#但是真誠才是最大本領<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/LungMunCafe/photos/a.880096878721797/3423457844385675/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLungMunCafe%2Fphotos%2Fa.880096878721797%2F3423457844385675%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInKZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=0a5ca5e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/LungMunCafe/photos/a.880096878721797/3423457844385675/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"b1ebfee1fe3f6ade395b778778c4c079005e895d","tid":2164684,"uid":7391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T10:40:08.000Z","msg":"張老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a998a3ad7b12a2cceb7ae38c0237699ea79ffb","tid":2164684,"uid":4599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T10:45:22.000Z","msg":"正呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />